  "detailed_description": "In Mad Geometry you solve puzzles by reshaping your own shape between cube and sphere. On each level there is simple rule: You are what you collect. All the puzzles emerge from this rule, which come together to tell story about the transformations caused by life. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n    • Dynamic but simple music <br />\r\n    • Procedurally generated boards<br />\r\n    • 8 worlds with 5 levels each<br />\r\n    • Inspired by classic puzzle games",
